    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Building material comprising roughly squared stone blocks of different sizes laid in courses. The horizontal and vertical joints do not line up consistently and smaller stones may be used to fill in gaps.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
